<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="keywords" content="">
    <link rel="icon" href="favicon.ico">
    <title>Fredyang's Blog</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "blog" %>
    <!-- HTML5 shim and Respond.js for IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="http://cdn.bootcss.com/html5shiv/3.7.0/html5shiv.js"></script>
      <script src="http://cdn.bootcss.com/respond.js/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
  </head>

  <body>

    <div class="blog-masthead">
      <div class="container blog-name">
          <a href="/" style="color:#FFF; text-decoration:none;">Fredyang</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">

      <div class="row">

        <div class="col-sm-8 blog-main">

	  <%= yield %>

        </div><!-- /.blog-main -->

        <div class="col-sm-3 col-sm-offset-1 blog-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-module sidebar-module-inset">
            <h4>Categories</h4>
            <ol class="list-unstyled">
	      <% @categories.each do |category| %>
	      <li><%= link_to category.name, category_path(category) %></li>
	      <% end %>
            </ol>
          </div>
          <div class="sidebar-module sidebar-module-inset">
            <h4>About</h4>
            <p>
	       <div style="margin-bottom:5px;">编程是一门艺术和哲学，产品也一样；</div>
	       <div style="margin-bottom:5px;">这个博客是我的第一个RoR作品，从前台到后台，从开发到部署，麻雀虽小五脏俱全，开源地址：<a href="http://git.io/AzK7" target="_blank">http://git.io/AzK7</a></div>
	       欢迎交流shuky2000#163.com
	    </p>
          </div>	  
<!--
          <div class="sidebar-module">
            <h4>Elsewhere</h4>
            <ol class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="#">GitHub</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Twitter</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Facebook</a></li>
            </ol>
          </div>
-->
        </div><!-- /.blog-sidebar -->

      </div><!-- /.row -->

    </div><!-- /.container -->

    <div class="blog-footer">
      <p>
        <a href="#">Back to top</a>
      </p>      
      <p>京ICP备13047626号-4 &copy; 2015 Fredyang</p>
    </div>


    <script src="http://cdn.bootcss.com/jquery/2.1.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="http://cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
